  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/96357fb1e5f960c0f806bbe0ca839185.poster.avif?t=1744610161\" width=600 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/96357fb1e5f960c0f806bbe0ca839185.webm?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/96357fb1e5f960c0f806bbe0ca839185.mp4?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oppressed is a realistic single-player first-person shooter built using HDRP technology on the Unity game engine. It was made by an independent developer who loves horror thriller games. Bodycam camera and realistic gameplay give players an immersive experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This time the player will find himself in a dark, creepy, unsettling corridor full of anomalies. <strong>Perhaps he is not alone in these corridors.</strong> The player must overcome his inner fears, stay alert and carefully investigate the surroundings, solving riddles to discover the anomalies, discover the escape route and regain his freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An experience with a surprise ending...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/c5750fd7d73f3fa2cfee63db56cd72b5.poster.avif?t=1744610161\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/c5750fd7d73f3fa2cfee63db56cd72b5.webm?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/c5750fd7d73f3fa2cfee63db56cd72b5.mp4?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Story Sackground</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our protagonist Luke finds himself in a hallway with a gun on the floor, not knowing how he got there. He has no idea how and why he ended up here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The writing on the walls tells him to move through the corridors and find anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can Luke find out why he is in this dark and creepy corridor and, more importantly, how to get out of it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/631bd9b9a0778c19bd640483dd119072.poster.avif?t=1744610161\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/631bd9b9a0778c19bd640483dd119072.webm?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/631bd9b9a0778c19bd640483dd119072.mp4?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Key Features</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Bodycam perspective gives players a realistic and stimulating experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Free aiming system with authentic ADS and unlimited hand gestures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Thrilling and scary experience with immersive sound effects and realistic visuals that create a thrilling atmosphere</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-A suspenseful story with a surprise ending</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/96357fb1e5f960c0f806bbe0ca839185.poster.avif?t=1744610161\" width=600 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/96357fb1e5f960c0f806bbe0ca839185.webm?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/96357fb1e5f960c0f806bbe0ca839185.mp4?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oppressed is a realistic single-player first-person shooter built using HDRP technology on the Unity game engine. It was made by an independent developer who loves horror thriller games. Bodycam camera and realistic gameplay give players an immersive experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This time the player will find himself in a dark, creepy, unsettling corridor full of anomalies. <strong>Perhaps he is not alone in these corridors.</strong> The player must overcome his inner fears, stay alert and carefully investigate the surroundings, solving riddles to discover the anomalies, discover the escape route and regain his freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An experience with a surprise ending...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/c5750fd7d73f3fa2cfee63db56cd72b5.poster.avif?t=1744610161\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/c5750fd7d73f3fa2cfee63db56cd72b5.webm?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/c5750fd7d73f3fa2cfee63db56cd72b5.mp4?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Story Sackground</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our protagonist Luke finds himself in a hallway with a gun on the floor, not knowing how he got there. He has no idea how and why he ended up here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The writing on the walls tells him to move through the corridors and find anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can Luke find out why he is in this dark and creepy corridor and, more importantly, how to get out of it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/631bd9b9a0778c19bd640483dd119072.poster.avif?t=1744610161\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/631bd9b9a0778c19bd640483dd119072.webm?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261750/extras/631bd9b9a0778c19bd640483dd119072.mp4?t=1744610161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Key Features</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Bodycam perspective gives players a realistic and stimulating experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Free aiming system with authentic ADS and unlimited hand gestures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Thrilling and scary experience with immersive sound effects and realistic visuals that create a thrilling atmosphere</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-A suspenseful story with a surprise ending</p>",
